sentences: Kaspar Zehnder (born 27 August 1970 in Riggisberg, Canton of Bern) is a Swiss conductor and flutist.
From 1997 to 2006, he was an associate professor at and conductor of the Orchestra of the Bern Academy of Arts (Hochschule der KÃ¼nste Bern), where he focused on contemporary music.
Zehnder was chief conductor of the Prague Philharmonia from 2005 to 2008.
Since 2014, he is the music director of the Symphoniy Orchester Biel Solothurn.
He currently is the artistic director at the Murten Classics Festival.
